    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. At its heart is the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M-differential lock. Technical highlights include a documented VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe\u2014addressing the critical structural concerns of the chassis. The suspension retains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and high-speed damping characteristic of the E46 platform. While showing minor cosmetic patina commensurate with its age, the mechanical vitals remain robust, with a linear power band and exceptional pedal feel from the vacuum-assisted braking system. A driver-focused machine for the purist seeking analog feedback.",
